# Logging Rules

Log:

✓ Withdrawal Created

✓ Withdrawal Approved

✓ Withdrawal Rejected

✓ Withdrawal Completed

✓ Validation Failures

---

Never log:

✗ Bank Account Number (full)

✗ Tokens

✗ Secrets

✗ Sensitive personal data

---

# Privacy Rules

Mask bank account numbers in logs.

Example

```text
123456789
```

↓

```text
*****6789
```

---

# Performance Rules

Create indexes:

- user_id
- status
- created_at

---

Always paginate withdrawal history.

---

